Availability:Public
Title: Open World Tools
Crumbs:
Description: Tools designed to facilitate the creation of large outdoor environments.
Navigation:topic
SkillLevel:Intermediate
Version: 4.8
parent:Engine
order:9

![](T_OWT_Header_00.png)

During the 2015 Games Developer Conference Epic showed off to the world Unreal Engine 4's ability to render massive open worlds full of both flora and fauna.
With the release of Unreal Engine 4.8 the tools used to create this demo, referred to as the **Open World Tools**, are now available for use in your UE4 projects. 

[region:note]
Please note that the Open World Tools are still in an experimental state which means that you could run into bugs or stability issues while using the tools.
[/region]

